description: Unique identifier for the state. Two State elements with the same identifier will use the same state
The event of the child element that will the state handler bind to. Leave out to not pass event handler down
The prop key under which the state will be passed to, leave out to not pass props down

A lambda function ID which takes in an object with the shape of: {event: Event, previousState: TState} and must return the next state object. Will get called when the event with the specified eventKey is called on the child element
